pt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
<div class=3D"text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p><img src=3D"https://jakevdp.github.io/PythonDataScienceHandbook/figures/=
05.05-gaussian-NB.png" alt=3D"(run code in Appendix to generate image)">
<a href=3D"https://jakevdp.github.io/PythonDataScienceHandbook/06.00-figure=
-code.html#Gaussian-Naive-Bayes">figure source in Appendix</a></p>

</div>
</div>
