</div>

</div>

</div>
</div>

</div>
<div class=3D"cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class=3D"prom=
pt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
<div class=3D"text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p>For simplicity here, we will select just a few of these categories, and =
download the training and testing set:</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered">
<div class=3D"input">
<div class=3D"prompt input_prompt">In&nbsp;[8]:</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
    <div class=3D"input_area">
<div class=3D" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class=3D"n">c=
ategories</span> <span class=3D"o">=3D</span> <span class=3D"p">[</span><sp=
an class=3D"s1">'talk.religion.misc'</span><span class=3D"p">,</span> <span=
 class=3D"s1">'soc.religion.christian'</span><span class=3D"p">,</span>
              <span class=3D"s1">'sci.space'</span><span class=3D"p">,</spa=
n> <span class=3D"s1">'comp.graphics'</span><span class=3D"p">]</span>
<span class=3D"n">train</span> <span class=3D"o">=3D</span> <span class=3D"=
n">fetch_20newsgroups</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"n">sub=
set</span><span class=3D"o">=3D</span><span class=3D"s1">'train'</span><spa=
n class=3D"p">,</span> <span class=3D"n">categories</span><span class=3D"o"=
>=3D</span><span class=3D"n">categories</span><span class=3D"p">)</span>
<span class=3D"n">test</span> <span class=3D"o">=3D</span> <span class=3D"n=
">fetch_20newsgroups</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"n">subs=
et</span><span class=3D"o">=3D</span><span class=3D"s1">'test'</span><span =
class=3D"p">,</span> <span class=3D"n">categories</span><span class=3D"o">=
=3D</span><span class=3D"n">categories</span><span class=3D"p">)</span>
</pre></div>

</div>
</div>
</div>

</div>
<div class=3D"cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class=3D"prom=
pt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
<div class=3D"text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p>Here is a representative entry from the data:</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered">
<div class=3D"input">
<div class=3D"prompt input_prompt">In&nbsp;[9]:</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
    <div class=3D"input_area">
<div class=3D" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class=3D"nb">=
print</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"n">train</span><span c=
lass=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">data</span><span class=3D"p">[</span><=
span class=3D"mi">5</span><span class=3D"p">])</span>
</pre></div>

</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class=3D"output_wrapper">
<div class=3D"output">


<div class=3D"output_area">

<div class=3D"prompt"></div>


<div class=3D"output_subarea output_stream output_stdout output_text">
<pre>From: dmcgee@uluhe.soest.hawaii.edu (Don McGee)
