</div>
</div>

</div>
</div>

</div>
<div class=3D"cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class=3D"prom=
pt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
<div class=3D"text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p>In order to use this data for machine learning, we need to be able to co=
nvert the content of each string into a vector of numbers.
For this we will use the TF-IDF vectorizer (discussed in <a href=3D"https:/=
/jakevdp.github.io/PythonDataScienceHandbook/05.04-feature-engineering.html=
">Feature Engineering</a>), and create a pipeline that attaches it to a mul=
tinomial naive Bayes classifier:</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered">
<div class=3D"input">
<div class=3D"prompt input_prompt">In&nbsp;[10]:</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
    <div class=3D"input_area">
<div class=3D" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class=3D"kn">=
from</span> <span class=3D"nn">sklearn.feature_extraction.text</span> <span=
 class=3D"k">import</span> <span class=3D"n">TfidfVectorizer</span>
<span class=3D"kn">from</span> <span class=3D"nn">sklearn.naive_bayes</span=
> <span class=3D"k">import</span> <span class=3D"n">MultinomialNB</span>
<span class=3D"kn">from</span> <span class=3D"nn">sklearn.pipeline</span> <=
span class=3D"k">import</span> <span class=3D"n">make_pipeline</span>

<span class=3D"n">model</span> <span class=3D"o">=3D</span> <span class=3D"=
n">make_pipeline</span><span class=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"n">TfidfVec=
torizer</span><span class=3D"p">(),</span> <span class=3D"n">MultinomialNB<=
/span><span class=3D"p">())</span>
</pre></div>

</div>
</div>
</div>

</div>
<div class=3D"cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class=3D"prom=
pt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
<div class=3D"text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p>With this pipeline, we can apply the model to the training data, and pre=
dict labels for the test data:</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered">
<div class=3D"input">
<div class=3D"prompt input_prompt">In&nbsp;[11]:</div>
<div class=3D"inner_cell">
    <div class=3D"input_area">
<div class=3D" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class=3D"n">m=
odel</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">fit</span><span clas=
s=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"n">train</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><sp=
an class=3D"n">data</span><span class=3D"p">,</span> <span class=3D"n">trai=
n</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">target</span><span clas=
