class=3D"p">,</span> <span class=3D"n">model</span><span class=3D"o">=3D</s=
pan><span class=3D"n">model</span><span class=3D"p">):</span>
    <span class=3D"n">pred</span> <span class=3D"o">=3D</span> <span class=
=3D"n">model</span><span class=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">predict</spa=
n><span class=3D"p">([</span><span class=3D"n">s</span><span class=3D"p">])=
</span>
    <span class=3D"k">return</span> <span class=3D"n">train</span><span cla=
ss=3D"o">.</span><span class=3D"n">target_names</span><span class=3D"p">[</=
span><span class=3D"n">pred</span><span class=3D"p">[</span><span class=3D"=
mi">0</span><span class=3D"p">]]</span>
</pre></div>

